{"tid":809520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搭高鐵驚聞「女海鮮」！嚇得她直閉氣　卻讓男網友超好奇","createTime":"2018-09-07T08:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T09:12:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9b31ffe323144c803a4cc3e95cdee11f82c775","tid":809520,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"香港一名網友日前搭高鐵時，不料卻在車上聞到陣陣惡臭，結果回頭看卻發現是後座的女子，竟將雙腳踩在椅子上，且沒有穿內褲，濃濃的腳臭味混合「海鮮味」四處飄散，讓她直呼「超噁心」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/05/1529151-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F05%2F1529151-XXL.jpg&h=86a29be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友在《香港醬聞》發文表示，日前搭乘蘇州往上海的大陸高鐵，不料短短25分鐘車程，卻不斷聞到「怪味」從後方飄來，不過原PO完全無法形容該怪味，只能以「總之就是很難聞，又有點腐臭味」表示。結果她回頭一看，卻發現一名女子脫著鞋，將兩隻腳放在座位，且大大方方露出下半身，甚至沒有穿內褲。讓她「即刻閉氣」，強烈懷疑，聞到的怪味就是女子腳臭加「海鮮味」，並希望該行程可以快點結束。<br />\n<br />\n對此，許多網友看完照片，紛紛表示，「中國有句成語曰：如入鮑魚之肆，久而不聞其臭！在那地方&hellip;習慣了&hellip;.就好」、「唉！正有什麼用，臭就全毀了」、「傻眼！怎麼那麼趕」，不過也有網友好奇是什麼味，直呼「好想聞聞看」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=425540\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D425540&d=y3Nr2Xfmn7RCtyCHc53wQW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8aaadfe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D425540&h=7389d03c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=425540</a>"},{"pid":"a17669f0b65d517a4b168d657596640565847479","tid":809520,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"個形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f26590177ee41766b1ecbdbe667c067680c5661","tid":809520,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"真係臭蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s